collector.data
Class CellInt

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--collector.data.CellInt
All Implemented Interfaces:
Element
public class CellInt
extends java.lang.Object
implements Element

An Cell is the basic piece of data, always associated to a Field. It can be saved/read as xml, displayed as a String. It has a type, a data and its label comes from the Field.
